'''Heesen游艇'''是一家荷兰造船 企业，专业定制建造 超级游艇 。该企业建立于1978年，自创立起已经推出了170多艘游艇，其中有很多获得了国际大奖，被认为是全铝制游艇设计、建造与工程方面的世界领军者之一。<ref>{{cite news|title=SuperYacht of the week: 4YOU, Heesen's latest masterpiece|url=http://www.superyachttimes.com/editorial/3/article/id/4196|accessdate=18 February 2015|publisher=Superyacht Times|date=20 March 2010|language=en|archive-date=2015-03-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150305024434/http://www.superyachttimes.com/editorial/3/article/id/4196|dead-url=no}}</ref>

==历史==

Frans Heesen在1978年创立了Heesen游艇。<ref>{{cite news|title=Heesen Sirocco|url=http://www.thereviewmag.co.uk/heesen-sirocco/|accessdate=18 February 2015|publisher=The Review Mag|date=11 July 2014|language=en|archive-date=2015-01-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150103053623/http://www.thereviewmag.co.uk/heesen-sirocco/|dead-url=no}}</ref> Heesen是一位企业家，在塑料产业的成就众所周知。他购买了荷兰的斯特来克船厂（Striker Boats）造船场地，本想将其作为另一企业的备选地址，但后来他决定保留这一产业的船厂性质，并令其继续运营。<ref>{{cite news |title=Het pensioensbootje van Frans Heesen, rijk worden zonder studie en de smartphone straks |url=http://925.nl/archief/2012/05/04/het-pensioensbootje-van-frans-heesen-rijk-worden-zonder-studie-en-de-smartphone-straks-week-18 |accessdate=22 September 2014 |language=nl |archive-date=2015-01-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150103072202/http://925.nl/archief/2012/05/04/het-pensioensbootje-van-frans-heesen-rijk-worden-zonder-studie-en-de-smartphone-straks-week-18 |dead-url=no }}</ref> 购买厂址一年后， Heesen推出了20米（66英尺）的 Amigo, 这是Heesen建造的第一艘游艇。<ref>{{cite news|title=Frans Heesen, Best Business Person of the Year 2009|url=http://www.superyachts.com/news/frans-heesen-best-business-person-of-the-year-2009-220.htm|accessdate=18 February 2015|publisher=Superyachts|language=en|archive-date=2015-01-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150103062735/http://www.superyachts.com/news/frans-heesen-best-business-person-of-the-year-2009-220.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>
[[File:Amigo.JPG|thumb]]
1988年是Heesen游艇突破性的一年。美国企业家John Staluppi出资要求为其建造一艘时速能够超过50节的游艇。<ref>{{cite news|last1=Chrisnell|first1=Mark|title=Lunch with...superyacht owner John Staluppi|url=http://www.boatinternational.com/buy-and-own/superyacht-owners-experiences/lunch-with-superyacht-owner-john-staluppi/|accessdate=18 February 2015|publisher=Boat International|language=en|archive-date=2015-02-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150212143541/http://www.boatinternational.com/buy-and-own/superyacht-owners-experiences/lunch-with-superyacht-owner-john-staluppi/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=ElePhatFounder>{{cite news|title=Elephants of Luxury - Frans Heesen: Founder of Heesen Yachts|url=http://www.elephantlifestyle.com/frans-heesen-founder-of-heesen-yachts_351.html|accessdate=18 February 2015|publisher=Elephant Lifestyle|language=en|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130902072858/http://www.elephantlifestyle.com/frans-heesen-founder-of-heesen-yachts_351.html|archivedate=2013年9月2日}}</ref> 因此，Heesen建造了Octopussy，后来又更名为 Octopussy 007。这是一艘保持当时最快纪录的定制游艇，记录在案的最高时速为53.17节。<ref name=ElePhatFounder/>  多年后，另一家公司对其进行了改装和加长，由此带来的重量增加使它不能再跻身世界最快的游艇行列。到了1990年，Heesen建造了超过25艘超过27米 (89英尺)的游艇，成为世界定制游艇造船商领军者之一。<ref>{{cite news|last1=Dawson|first1=Dudley|title=Pershing 54 is an American Revolution |url=http://books.google.com/books?id=9JC1exE3blwC&pg=PA76&lpg=PA76&dq=Diaship+heesen&source=bl&ots=rFuN8jM6OG&sig=rkkPqFQI_PlKCYdKoUPHYOyeTec&hl=en&sa=X&ei=NPEiVJ38McmbyATVq4G4DQ&ved=0CB0Q6AEwADgK#v=onepage&q=Diaship%20heesen&f=false |accessdate=18 February 2015 |publisher=Yachting|date=August 1999|language=en}}</ref> 1991年，Heesen推出了曾用名El Corsario的游艇The Mirage，它被认为是Octopussy的姐妹设计。该船采用了三重射流作为推进力，并被Boat International  列为世界最快游艇的第十六位。<ref>{{cite web|title=Top 20 Fastest Yachts|url=http://www.boatinternational.com/yachts/the-register/top-20-fastest-yachts/?pg=2|website=Boat International|accessdate=18 February 2015|language=en|archive-date=2015-01-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150103052315/http://www.boatinternational.com/yachts/the-register/top-20-fastest-yachts/?pg=2|dead-url=no}}</ref> 该船巡航时速为45节，最高时速可达48节。

1992年，企业拓展了自身业务范围，涵盖了传统排水长距离钢制船体游艇的建造。推出的首艘该类游艇是与Oceanco合作的50米(160英尺) 机动游艇Achiever。<ref name=BIyachtsDutchsale>{{cite news|last1=MacLean|first1=Malcolm|title=Going Dutch - six Heesen motor yachts for sale|url=http://www.boatinternational.com/yacht-features/going-dutch-six-heesen-motor-yachts-for-sale/|accessdate=18 February 2015|publisher=Boat International|language=en|archive-date=2015-01-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150103070902/http://www.boatinternational.com/yacht-features/going-dutch-six-heesen-motor-yachts-for-sale/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

1996年 Heesen已经因为早期建造的斯特来克赛渔艇著称，并通过交付37米(121英尺) Obsession开始了大型赛渔艇建造，该游艇最高时速可达33节。<ref>{{cite news|last1=de Waard|first1=Merijn|title=Heesen's superyacht Obsessions in D-Marin Didim|url=http://www.superyachttimes.com/editorial/24/article/id/12049|accessdate=18 February 2015|publisher=Superyacht Times|date=3 April 2014|language=en|archive-date=2015-03-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150331040032/http://www.superyachttimes.com/editorial/24/article/id/12049|dead-url=no}}</ref> 当时她是世界最大的赛渔艇。<ref name=BIyachtsDutchsale/> Heesen于2003年进一步拓展业务，并于同年推出了3700和 4400游艇系列。<ref name=BIyachtsDutchsale/> 该次业务拓展包括建造新的造船设施，企业每年有能力建造八艘游艇。<ref name=BIyachtsDutchsale/>
[[File:Fort-lauderdale-man-of-steel.JPG|thumb]]
Heesen游艇出现在2011年出版的Andrew Rogers的著作《M/Y AlumerciA之旅 》当中。这本书记录了这艘由Heesen建造的著名游艇从2001年到2010年进行的旅程。2013年, Heesen推出了65米 (213英尺)速排游艇Galactica Star, 这是一艘定制游艇，最高时速为28.8节。<ref>{{cite news|title=Forget Iron Man and Star Trek|url=http://www.yachtingmagazine.com/forget-iron-man-and-star-trek|accessdate=18 February 2015|publisher=Yachting Magazine|date=10 May 2013|language=en|archive-date=2017-10-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171011235520/http://www.yachtingmagazine.com/forget-iron-man-and-star-trek|dead-url=no}}</ref> 该船已获得九项大奖，其中包括世界超级游艇大奖赛最佳半排50米以上级游艇奖[12]。Heesen还在2011年推出了Satori，这艘游艇也获得了世界超级游艇大奖赛的奖项。<ref name=BIyachtsDutchsale/> Frans Heesen在创建Heesen游艇35年后，于2012年退休<ref name=ElePhatFounder/>

2014年，Heesen游艇接手了迄今最大的项目，船长70米(230英尺)的铝制速排游艇。<ref name=MYN2014>{{cite news|title=Kometa, by Heesen Yachts: October 2014 Motoryacht video|url=http://megayachtnews.com/2014/10/kometa-heesen-yachts-october-2014-motoryacht-video/#axzz3FZKNs2M0|accessdate=18 February 2015|publisher=Mega Yacht News|date=1 October 2014|language=en|archive-date=2015-01-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150103093114/http://megayachtnews.com/2014/10/kometa-heesen-yachts-october-2014-motoryacht-video/#axzz3FZKNs2M0|dead-url=no}}</ref> 该船名为Project Kometa，是与Espen Oeino合作建造的，最高时速30节。该船将于2016年交付。<ref name=MYN2014/>

